<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/10069865-deborah">Deborah</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I love the Artemis Fowl series. I enjoy it for what it is, fun reading. If you like good humor and some suspense, then yes, you may like Artemis Fowl.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I love the Artemis Fowl series. I enjoy it for what it is, fun reading. If you like good humor and some suspense, then yes, you may like Artemis Fowl. If you are an intense type of person, you may not enjoy it so much. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
