<div id="review_3805169392" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3805169392" />
    <a title="Beatrice" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/69793229-beatrice"><img alt="Beatrice" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1613946235p2/69793229.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3805169392?book_show_action=true">Jan 30, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Beatrice" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Beatrice" href="/user/show/69793229-beatrice">Beatrice</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/69793229-beatrice?shelf=reviews">reviews</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/69793229-beatrice?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3805169392" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11151839635594614066">This was a little disappointing considering how much i liked the last Artemis Fowl book I read. I thought the beginning of the story was really interesting and fun to read, but then it just got a little boring. Honestly, it reminded me too much of the Arctic Incident and i felt it was missing that new and original feature. I mean, Artemis is still such a cool character to read about. But I hope I will like the next ones more. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


